    <item>
      <title>[두근두근 뇌 운동] [2566] 로꾸거 암송클럽</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/2025/02/21/TG6QQIDUGBG5VARW3DTPVZ6WUU/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/2025/02/21/TG6QQIDUGBG5VARW3DTPVZ6WUU/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
